    `reference (N=500000)      ≈ ${truth.toFixed(12)}\n\n`+
    `advantage: ${(Math.abs(naive-truth)/Math.max(1e-20,Math.abs(em-truth))).toExponential(2)}× fewer terms would the naïve sum need?\n`+
    `(For s=${s.toFixed(2)} near 1, naïve needs N ≈ 10^{${Math.ceil(1/(s-1)*3)}} for 6-digit accuracy — EM reaches the same with N = ${N}.)`;
}
